Sec. 41.028. EXEMPTIONS FOR PRODUCERS. The original referendum
and subsequent biennial board elections may provide exemptions for
producers within the boundaries described in the petition if the
exemptions are included in full written form on the election ballot
and are approved by two-thirds or more of those voting in the
election.
Acts 1981, 67th Leg., p. 1084, ch. 388, Sec. 1, eff. Sept. 1, 1981.

